Revised [memo.md](~/Documents/github/resources/ai-for-research/demos/orchestration-lab/runs/advisor/t3-codex/memo.md) (384 words) and [sensitivity-table.md](~/Documents/github/resources/ai-for-research/demos/orchestration-lab/runs/advisor/t3-codex/sensitivity-table.md).

The revision:
- Uses the requested bounded headline claim.
- States plainly that re-referencing cannot change invariant level-mean ranges.
- Avoids unsupported rank ordering against commuting time.
- Documents respondent-clustered uncertainty and the reliability adjustment.
- Adds all racial-composition marginal means and its invariant range.
- Corrects the reversed AMCE CI formatting.

I reran [script.R](~/Documents/github/resources/ai-for-research/demos/orchestration-lab/runs/advisor/t3-codex/script.R), which also regenerated and visually checked [sensitivity.png](~/Documents/github/resources/ai-for-research/demos/orchestration-lab/runs/advisor/t3-codex/figures/sensitivity.png).
